Guest-side clipboard agent for macOS virtual machines hosted by
Apple's Virtualization framework. Bridges the guest's NSPasteboard
to the host's clipboard by speaking the SPICE vd_agent protocol over
the virtio-serial port exposed by VZSpiceAgentPortAttachment.

Depends on:
  - SpiceProtocol       (MIT, Spooky Labs) — wire format
  - SpiceSerialTransport (MIT, Spooky Labs) — async tty I/O

No source code from SPICE reference implementations (spice-vdagent,
spice-gtk, utmapp/vd_agent) was copied or derived. See
../SpiceProtocol/docs/SPEC_ATTRIBUTION.md for the full chain of
custody from the public SPICE specification to this implementation.
